gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Celtics 119, Bucks 116
gameRecap.excerpt: The Celtics hang on and defeat the Bucks, 119-116. Jaylen Brown recorded 26 points, eight assists, and two rebounds for the Celtics, with Jayson Tatum adding 23 points and 11 rebounds in the victory. Brook Lopez tallied a game-high 28 points along with seven rebounds for the Bucks in the losing effort. The Celtics improve to 12-3 in the regular season, while the Bucks fall to 10-5.
